org.springframework.cli
Class SpringCli

java.lang.Object
  org.springframework.cli.SpringCli

public class SpringCli
extends Object

Spring Command Line Interface. This is the main entry-point for the Spring command line application. This class will parse input arguments and delegate to a suitable Command implementation based on the first argument.

The '-d' and '--debug' switches are handled by this class, however, most argument parsing is left to the Command implementation.

Author:
Phillip Webb
See Also:
